WEBVTT

00:00.688 --> 00:03.310
Alex has to be better, or we're
gonna be in serious trouble here.

00:03.435 --> 00:04.253
She will be.

00:04.378 --> 00:07.235
I'm letting everyone down, and
I don't get drunk when I'm sad.

00:07.360 --> 00:08.576
I sleep with boys.

00:08.701 --> 00:09.677
You want to get out of here?

00:09.802 --> 00:11.078
My name is Millicent.

00:11.203 --> 00:13.647
I keep telling everybody I'm fine,

00:13.772 --> 00:15.249
and I'm not fine.

00:15.374 --> 00:16.983
So, let me get this straight.

00:17.108 --> 00:18.918
You don't want to make a record
because it's too personal?

00:19.043 --> 00:21.387
- That's right.
- Personal sells albums.

00:21.512 --> 00:22.288
So, make a record with me.

00:22.413 --> 00:24.776
I loved you so much, Sara.

00:24.901 --> 00:28.537
You were perfect with me...
and you always will be.

00:30.232 --> 00:31.099
Are you okay, mom?

00:31.224 --> 00:32.383
I have cancer.

00:32.508 --> 00:35.049
- Oh, no, no, no.
- It's pancreatic.

00:35.174 --> 00:36.745
So I've accepted it.

00:36.870 --> 00:38.027
You're giving up.

00:38.152 --> 00:39.691
No, I am not giving up.

00:39.816 --> 00:41.174
Maybe Quinn can take a picture of it.

00:41.299 --> 00:42.667
We can just add it to this stupid box.

00:42.792 --> 00:45.194
Taylor. Tay.

